##General binds
<tab> move panels
p pull
P push
<1-#> select panel
<S-=> maximize panels

## <Files>
<space> stage item item
a stage all
c commit message
d discard changes (file)
D hard reset menu (can this disable or have a warning?)
<Enter> view file; edit husks
s stash
S stash menu (e.g. staged items)

## Branch
o open pull request (opens browser)
<enter> enter patching
  <space> select parts of patch
  <C-P> (in branch area) patch menu
f fetch
r rebase (to branch/master)?

## <commits>
c Cherry picking
e Interactive rebase
  s squash
  p pick
  m (merge)
  <C-J> / <C-K> reordering commits
  A ammend commit with staged file(s)
<Enter> view files of commit
F fixup?

(merge conflict)
  <Enter> (in merge conflict) choose side to pick
  b pick both
